title: Openscapes JupyterHub Access
text:
Openscapes JupyterHub Access 

Openscapes supports organizations that are starting to explore cloud computing by partnering with 2i2c, who design and administer a global network of community hubs. Openscapes Hubs provide a place for people to teach workshops and experiment with cloud-based workflows.
